  "title": "Senior/Finance Admin Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Perform accounting duties such as bank reconciliation, A/R, A/P, invoicing, data entry, invoicing, etc.</li>\n  <li>Handle general administrative duties</li>\n  <li>Perform counter duties on rotation basis (e.g. collection of payments, attending to resident enquiries, etc.)</li>\n  <li>Assist in preparing monthly reports, perform day-end closing, prepare payment vouchers &amp; reminder notices</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>GCE 'O' / 'A' Level / NITEC/HNITEC/Diploma in Accounting / Business Studies or related courses</li>\n  <li>Proficient in Microsoft Office (Word and Excel)</li>\n  <li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n</ul>",
